input: The cow is big. The cow needs the tiger. The dog is big. The dog is kind. The dog needs the cow. The dog sees the rabbit. The dog visits the tiger. The rabbit needs the tiger. The tiger is big. The tiger is cold. The tiger needs the cow. The tiger needs the rabbit. If someone is cold then they visit the tiger. If someone sees the tiger then the tiger visits the dog. If someone is kind and they visit the tiger then the tiger visits the rabbit. If someone needs the tiger then the tiger is big. If someone visits the tiger and they see the rabbit then the tiger visits the rabbit. If someone visits the rabbit and the rabbit sees the cow then the rabbit is cold. If someone visits the tiger then they visit the cow. If someone visits the rabbit then the rabbit sees the cow. If someone sees the rabbit then the rabbit is kind. Question: The rabbit visits the cow.?
output:
universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant Cow : obj
constant Dog : obj
constant Rabbit : obj
constant Tiger : obj

constant Big : obj → Prop
constant Needs : obj → obj → Prop
constant Sees : obj → obj → Prop
constant Visits : obj → obj → Prop
constant Cold : obj → Prop
constant Kind : obj → Prop

axiom T1 : Big Cow
axiom T2 : Needs Cow Tiger
axiom T3 : Big Dog
axiom T4 : Kind Dog
axiom T5 : Needs Dog Cow
axiom T6 : Sees Dog Rabbit
axiom T7 : Visits Dog Tiger
axiom T8 : Needs Rabbit Tiger
axiom T9 : Big Tiger
axiom T10 : Cold Tiger
axiom T11 : Needs Tiger Cow
axiom T12 : Needs Tiger Rabbit

axiom R1 : ∀ x : obj, Cold x → Visits x Tiger
axiom R2 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Tiger → Visits Tiger Dog
axiom R3 : ∀ x : obj, Kind x ∧ Visits x Tiger → Visits Tiger Rabbit
axiom R4 : ∀ x : obj, Needs x Tiger → Big Tiger
axiom R5 : ∀ x : obj, Visits x Tiger ∧ Sees x Rabbit → Visits Tiger Rabbit
axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Visits x Rabbit ∧ Sees Rabbit Cow → Cold Rabbit
axiom R7 : ∀ x : obj, Visits x Tiger → Visits x Cow
axiom R8 : ∀ x : obj, Visits x Rabbit → Sees Rabbit Cow
axiom R9 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Rabbit → Kind Rabbit

theorem rabbit_visits_cow : Visits Rabbit Cow :=
begin
  apply R7,
  apply R1,
  apply R6 Rabbit,
  split,
  apply R5 Dog,
  split,
  exact T7,
  exact T6,
  apply R8,
  apply R5 Dog,
  split,
  exact T7,
  exact T6,
end

-- The answer is True
